testcase.title: To verify NumberOfSites Column is after RecruitmentStatus column in exportTrialResults

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "format = MS_EXCEL and query = cancer and offset = 0 and hits = 10 and expectedValues = exportTrialResults14432_1_1.xls" as parameter to "exportTrialResultsv2" operation
check the requested file is found in the following path "exportTrialResults14432_1_1.xls"
I should find "Number Of Sites" column after "Recruitment Status" column in the exported file
